
= Method:createQueries = 

_ sql dumper for symmetric data _

Exports csv data into sql. Only when the headers match all
records length (symmetric)

  # *Argument* _string_  $tablename the tablename to use for inserts
  # *Argument* _array_   $headers   the headers to use, if none given
all headers are included by default

  * *Visibility*  public

  * *Returns* array
  * *Also see* symmetric(), asymmetry()
